model.dek: Kate Maxwell reports on the best stores, boutiques, and markets in London's East End including Aubin and Wills, 11 Boundary, and Broadway Market.
model.hed: The Best Shopping in London's East End

items.caption: For art that you can buy and take away, there is the **[Nelly Duff](http://www.nellyduff.com/) **gallery on Columbia Road, with an eclectic selection and a hip curator.

items.title:
2. Ryantown

3. Suck and Chew
items.caption: Find intricate paper cutouts, prints, hand-printed cushion covers, and mugs by illustrator Rob Ryan at **[Ryantown](http://ryantownshop.blogspot.com/)** (pictured) (No. 126; 20-7613-1510) and old-fashioned candy in glass jars—rhubarb and custard boiled sweets, “gob stoppers” (jawbreakers), licorice, and lollipops—plus vintage commemorative china and tin boxes—at [**Suck and Chew**](http://www.suckandchew.co.uk/) (No. 130; 20-8983-3504).

items.title: 4. Labour and Wait
items.caption: On Redchurch Street, **[Labor and Wait](http://www.labourandwait.co.uk/)** sells classic British hardware and kitchen products: Brown Betty teapots, enamel mugs, church candles, plus clothing like Guernsey jumpers and Breton tops (No. 85; 20-7729-6253).

items.title: 5. Aubin & Wills
items.caption: The **[Aubin & Wills](http://www.aubinandwills.com/en-gb/home)** flagship has a cinema and a gallery in addition to preppy men’s and women’s clothing (No. 64-66; 20-3487-0066).

items.title: 6. 11 Boundary
items.caption: Opposite the Boundary Hotel, **[11 Boundary](http://www.11boundary.com/)** stocks homegrown labels like Cocorose ballet pumps and Madeleine Thompson cashmeres (20-7033-0310).

items.title: 7. Comfort Station
items.caption: Cheshire Street, off Brick Lane, and Calvert Avenue, off Arnold Circus, are other indie shop hot spots: Check out the jewelry and accessories at **[Comfort Station](http://www.comfortstation.co.uk/)** (22 Cheshire St.; 20-7033-9099).

items.title: 8. Mawi
items.caption: And hit **[Mawi](http://www.mawi.co.uk/US/)** for fierce skull-adorned baubles (11 Calvert Ave.).
